RUNTIME LIBRARY EXCEPTION

Programs written in Simplex are NOT subject to the AGPL-3.0 copyleft
requirements. You may license your own Simplex programs under any terms
you choose.

See the RUNTIME-EXCEPTION file for the full exception text.

